data.description: THE APPRAISAL CAME BACK AT THE NEW LIST PRICE.  This home offers uniqueness that is full of possibilities!  It comes to you with R-3 zoning, which offers the opportunity to take advantage of the fullness of the provisions of same.  Owner added a half bathroom on the main floor, opting to convert the dining area to more utilitarian use and modifying the kitchen for eat-in space.  There are 2 bedrooms upstairs, separated by the full bathroom and a den/study.  The character of this property has been preserved and there is room for expansion.  This is a "Must See" property that offers more than the existing floor plan.  Bring your imagination and vision along with your offer and create a masterpiece in this reportedly quite neighborhood!
